```plantuml
@startuml LouisvilleMetro_WazeCCPProcessor

actor WazeCCPUser

participant "Waze Data Feed" as WDF
participant "waze-data-download\nLambda" as WDD
participant "S3 Bucket\n(Data Lake)" as S3
participant "waze-data-process\nLambda" as WDP
participant "SQS Queue" as SQS
participant "waze-data-alerts-processing\nLambda" as WDAP
participant "waze-data-jams-processing\nLambda" as WDJP
participant "waze-data-irregularities-processing\nLambda" as WDIP
participant "Aurora PostgreSQL\nDatabase" as DB
participant "waze-db-initialize\nLambda" as WDI
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "waze-data-api\nLambda" as WDA

WazeCCPUser -> WDF: Request Data
WDF -> WDD: Provide Waze Data URL
WDD -> S3: Store JSON Data

S3 -> WDP: Trigger Data Processing
WDP -> SQS: Queue Processing Tasks
SQS -> WDAP: Process Alerts Data
SQS -> WDJP: Process Jams Data
SQS -> WDIP: Process Irregularities Data

WDAP -> DB: Store Alerts
WDJP -> DB: Store Jams
WDIP -> DB: Store Irregularities

WDI -> DB: Initialize/Update Schema

WazeCCPUser -> APIGW: Query Processed Data
APIGW -> WDA: Handle Request
WDA -> DB: Access Processed Data
DB -> WDA: Return Data
WDA -> APIGW: Respond with Data
APIGW -> WazeCCPUser: Deliver Data

@enduml
```